Used to slow and blind the Terrors at night.

Shoot the targets in the highlighted order. The last target provides the reward.

Stand in the ring to acquire the reward.

Someone stands on the pad whilst the other person collects the reward.
Jemand steht auf dem Pad, während die andere Person die Belohnung erhält.
